txt.en: Your mission is to find and defeat Rauzhúl, the Orc captain defending Shathur-munzu.\n\nSpeak to Hórin to travel to Shathur-munzu.

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].\n\n'Shathur-munzu, the abandoned fort in Duskenvale, had been quiet since the departure of the warg chieftain, but the scouts have reported a new Orkish presence. We cannot allow them to set up a base to the south and surround us in the battle to come! Break their defences!'
DNT - 'When you are ready, the scouts will lead you to Shathur-munzu. Good luck!'
'Well done! Though the great prize of Gundabad stands in front of us, we must remember to also protect our rear!'
The mission is complete.\n\nSpeak to Hórin for your reward.
You must find a way to breach a barrier to reach your mission objective.
The Orcs and Wargs have returned to Shathur-munzu, attempting to set up a new base south of the warfront….\n\nYour mission is to find and defeat Rauzhúl, the Orc captain defending Shathur-munzu.
You have been tasked with dispatching the Orc captain defending Shathur-munzu.
